header.gameNote: ROSE BOWL GAME PRESENTED BY NORTHWESTERN MUTUAL - CFP SEMIFINAL

videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds Dimitri Flowers on 2 straight plays, both resulting in first downs for Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Mayfield hits Flowers on back-to back plays

videos.description: Oklahoma's Baker Mayfield rolls right and finds Marquise Brown in the end zone to go up 7-0 early in the Rose Bowl. Mayfield opens 4-for-4 for 63 yards.
videos.headline: Mayfield hits wide open Brown for TD to open Rose Bowl

videos.description: Nick Chubb turns upfield, shows off his speed and picks up a nice gain for Georgia.
videos.headline: Chubb breaks off tough 25-yard run

videos.description: Georgia answers Oklahoma with a 13-yard touchdown strike by Jake Fromm to Sony Michel.
videos.headline: Fromm finds Michel for 13-yard TD

videos.description: Rodney Anderson burst up the middle and powers his way downfield to put Oklahoma in the red zone.
videos.headline: Anderson breaks off 45-yard run

videos.description: Rodney Anderson plows through two defenders as he crosses the goal line to give Oklahoma its second touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Anderson powers in 9-yard TD run for OU

videos.description: After Rodrigo Blankenship's kick just goes wide left, Baker Mayfield makes a hand gesture towards his neck.
videos.headline: Mayfield rubs it in after Georgia's missed FG

videos.description: Oklahoma's Rodney Anderson sneaks through a hole and burst free 41 yards for his second rushing touchdown of the Rose Bowl.
videos.headline: Anderson breaks loose for a 41-yard TD run

videos.description: Sony Michel gets through the defense and outruns everyone for the Georgia touchdown.
videos.headline: Michel breaks off 75-yard TD

videos.description: Baker Mayfield completes a pass for 29 yards to Mark Andrews to set an Oklahoma school record for total yards in a season.
videos.headline: Mayfield sets Oklahoma school record for total yards

videos.description: Baker Mayfield dumps it off to CeeDee Lamb who follows his blocks to pick up a first down for the Sooners. OU would eventually make a field goal.
videos.headline: Oklahoma's 3rd-down conversion leads to FG

videos.description: Nick Chubb burst up the middle, gets to the outside on his way to flipping the field for Georgia.
videos.headline: Chubb shows off his speed on 45-yard run

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trey Sermon cuts through a hole, runs over a Georgia defender for extra yardage.
videos.headline: Sermon trucks UGA defender on 31-yard run

videos.description: After a completion from Baker Mayfield, Marquise Brown shows off his elusiveness in the open field to put Oklahoma in the red zone.
videos.headline: Brown shows off jets on 45-yard reception

videos.description: Oklahoma's trick play leads to a Baker Mayfield touchdown reception from CeeDee Lamb.
videos.headline: Mayfield catches first career TD just before half

videos.description: Oklahoma head coach Lincoln Riley discusses the reasoning for a squib kick just before halftime as well as what to look forward to in the second half of the Rose Bowl.
videos.headline: Lincoln Riley explains squib kick at end of dominating half

videos.description: Rodrigo Blankenship makes the longest field goal in Rose Bowl history as the first half ends.
videos.headline: Blankenship's 55-yard FG sets Rose Bowl record

videos.description: Baker Mayfield throws a touchdown and catches a score on some trickery late in the second quarter to give the Sooners a commanding lead over Georgia at the half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Mayfield leads OU to lead at half) 2018/1/1 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Mayfield leads OU to lead at half

videos.description: Heisman winner Baker Mayfield throws for 200 yards and a TD and catches a score to give OU a 14-point lead at the half over Georgia.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Mayfield thriving on big stage at Rose Bowl) 2018/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mayfield thriving on big stage at Rose Bowl

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart says his Bulldogs played a poor first half but their offense is keeping them in the game.
videos.headline: Smart not happy with UGA's first-half performance

videos.description: Georgia's Nick Chubb takes on multiple Oklahoma defenders before breaking free for a 50-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Chubb breaks tackles on scintillating 50-yard TD run

videos.description: Rodney Anderson runs up the middle and uses  a nice cutback to convert on 3rd down for Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Anderson follows his blocks for 25-yard run

videos.description: Georgia's D'Andre Walker sacks Baker Mayfield then imitates Mayfield's arm-flailing celebration.
videos.headline: Walker mocks Mayfield after back-to-back sacks

videos.description: Baker Mayfield runs upfield and appears to get hit late with a knee by Julian Rochester.
videos.headline: Mayfield takes knee to midsection on run

videos.description: Georgia's Sony Michel runs 38 yards for a game-tying touchdown late in the third quarter. Michel averaged 23.7 yards per carry on his first six runs.
videos.headline: Michel bursts free for his third TD of the Rose Bowl

videos.description: Georgia goes up by 7 early in the 4th quarter on a Jake Fromm laser to Javon Wims.
videos.headline: Fromm throws a dart to take 4th-quarter lead

videos.description: Baker Mayfield throws up the jumpball and CeeDee Lamb comes down with it for a gain of 36 yards.
videos.headline: Lamb outjumps defender to make catch

videos.description: Baker Mayfield buys time, then throws a strike to Dimitri Flowers in the back of the end zone to tie Georgia at 38.
videos.headline: Mayfield connects with Flowers to tie Rose Bowl

videos.description: Sony Michel loses the ball after a hard hit and Steven Parker picks it up, stays in bounds and returns it for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Oklahoma defense gets scoop-and-score TD

videos.description: Jake Fromm dodges an Oklahoma defender in the backfield, scrambles forward, then completes a pass to Sony Michel for a 17-yard gain.
videos.headline: Fromm avoids sack before clutch first down

videos.description: Nick Chubb takes a direct snap and follows his blocks to score the game-tying touchdown late in the 4th quarter for Georgia.
videos.headline: Chubb scores TD after taking snap

videos.description: Austin Seibert 33-yard field goal ties the game with Georgia and keeps Oklahoma's season alive.
videos.headline: Seibert's FG forces 2nd OT

videos.description: Georgia's Lorenzo Carter leaps up and blocks Oklahoma's field goal attempt in double overtime.
videos.headline: Carter blocks OU's kick in second OT

videos.description: Sony Michel takes a direct snap to the house to win the game for Georgia, and the Bulldogs advance to the College Football National Championship.
videos.headline: Michel scores game-winning TD for Georgia in 2OT

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart breaks down his feelings about advancing to the College Football National Championship.
videos.headline: Smart proud of his Bulldogs' attitude

videos.description: Both Georgia QB Jake Fromm and LB Roquan Smith discuss the team's 2nd-half comeback as well as going back to Georgia for the College Football National Championship.
videos.headline: Fromm encouraged UGA to 'believe'

videos.description: Kirby Smart and the Georgia Bulldogs receive the Leishman Trophy for winning the Rose Bowl.
videos.headline: Smart excited for chance to win title in Georgia

videos.description: After rushing for 181 yards and scoring 4 total touchdowns, Georgia RB Sony Michel is named offensive player of game in the Rose Bowl.
videos.headline: Michel credits a 'team effort' on scoring game-winning TD

videos.description: Georgia overcomes a 14-point deficit in the 2nd half and beats Oklahoma 54-48 on a walk-off touchdown in 2OT.

videos.description: The 2018 Rose Bowl provided some of the most memorable plays in college football history.

videos.headline: Georgia comes out on top in wild 2018 Rose Bowl

videos.description: Georgia's Roquan Smith receives the defensive player of the game award in the Rose Bowl after posting 11 tackles and 1 for a loss.
videos.headline: Smith awarded defensive player of the Rose Bowl

videos.description: Baker Mayfield returned for his senior season to win it all, so he left the Rose Bowl with no words to describe the Sooners' loss.

videos.description: Baker Mayfield holds back tears as he talks about playing his last game at Oklahoma and what Lincoln Riley means to him.

videos.description: In the highest-scoring Rose Bowl ever that featured six lead changes, Sony Michel scored four times including the game-winner to overcome Baker Mayfield's big game in double overtime.

videos.description: Oklahoma head coach Lincoln Riley says it's tough to describe his feelings after losing to Georgia in the College Football Playoff.
